澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻 综合报道今天上午，上海市公共卫生临床中心再度传来好消息：22名患者痊愈出院，包括3名重症患者。
This morning, the Shanghai Public Health Clinic again reported good news: 22 patients were discharged from hospital, including three seriously ill patients.
截至目前，治愈出院率已超74%。
To date, the cure rate has exceeded 74 per cent.
备受期待的“上海方案”几时出炉？在上海医疗救治专家组组长、华山医院感染科主任张文宏看来，上海的方案并不是停留在纸上的，而是写在病人身上，治疗方案只有写在病人身上，才认为这个治疗方案是正确的。
When is the much-anticipated "Shanghai Plan" coming out? According to Zhang Wenhong, the head of the Shanghai Medical Treatment Expert Group and director of infection at Huashan Hospital, the Shanghai plan is not a paper one, but one written on patients.
“所以，这些病人出院了，我认为上海的方案就出台了。
"So these patients are out of the hospital and I think the plan for Shanghai is in place.
”Play目前，上海的患者中年龄大的较多，更容易引起病情进展，这也给医疗团队带来更大挑战。
More patients in Shanghai are now older and more likely to develop the condition, which poses a greater challenge for the medical team.
那么对于重症患者、危重症患者的治疗方案，上海又有什么特点？Play张文宏在接受记者采访时表示，“我跟你讲你一定听不懂，因为我们读的书不一样，我讲的每一个汉字你都能听明白，但不会知道是什么意思。
"I'm telling you you can't understand it because we're reading a different book and you can hear every Chinese character I speak, but you don't know what it means," Zhang Wenhong told reporters.
但有一句话你一定能听懂。
But there's one thing you must understand.
”随后他用这一句话总结了上海重症患者治疗方案的特点：即在上海市政府、卫健委的统一协调下，把上海市所有的优势资源、多学科团队全部集中在这里，一起救治。
"Then he summed up the characteristics of the treatment plan for the seriously ill in Shanghai with this sentence:" Under the unified coordination of the Shanghai Municipal Government and the Fitness and Hygiene Committee, all Shanghai's superior resources and multidisciplinary teams are concentrated here for joint treatment.
而就在昨晚，张文宏还在上海一活动中，担任了主讲嘉宾，与网友分享自己的书单，探讨疫情防控期间如何正常生活。
And just last night, Zhang Wenhong was a guest speaker at an event in Shanghai, sharing his book list with netizens and discussing how to live a normal life during disease prevention and control.
在将近一小时的直播时间里，张文宏又爆出了哪些金句？小编为你整理了下：华山医院感染科主任张文宏教授。
In nearly an hour of live broadcast time, Zhang Wenhong burst out what gold sentence for you: Huashan Hospital Infection Director Professor Zhang Wenhong.
澎湃新闻记者 邓朝键 图“ 防火防盗防同事上海熬过了14天的节点，大部分人经受了考验，确诊人数断崖式下跌。
Peng Pai journalist Deng Chaokey Map "Fire Prevention Anti-Burglary Co-worker Shanghai has stood the test for 14 days, most of the people have been tested, confirmed the number of cliff-style fall.
他表示，大家可以慢慢地在可控的范围内出来走走，但必须戴着口罩。
'People can walk out in a controlled fashion, but they have to wear masks, 'he said.
“还得保持着警惕的心态，不要到处瞎玩，不要摘下口罩聊天，避免一起吃饭，取消不必要的活动。
"Stay alert and don't fool around, take off your mask and chat, avoid eating together and cancel unnecessary activities.
正常生活正在慢慢回归，但是还没有到为所欲为的地步。
Normal life is slowly returning, but not to the point of doing what it pleases.
张文宏建议大家，做好自我防护，戴好口罩，勤洗手。
Zhang Wenhong recommends that we do a good job of self-protection, wearing masks, frequent hand washing.
同时他还强调了之前刷屏的“金句”：“防火防盗防同事”。
He also highlighted the previous brush screen "golden sentence": "Fire-proof anti-theft colleagues.
此前报道《“段子手男神”张文宏，又有金句了！》“ 通过看无聊电视剧缓解疲劳疫情当前，很多一线医务工作者，一天工作时间要超过15、16个小时。
Many front-line health workers work more than 15 or 16 hours a day by watching boring TV dramas to alleviate the fatigue of the epidemic.
在谈到如何休息时，张文宏透露，外科医生回家深更半夜，回家的感觉就是“葛优躺”。
In talking about how to rest, Zhang Wenhong revealed that surgeons go home in the middle of the night, home feeling is "Ge You Lie."
他说，“像钟南山教授一身肌肉一样很少见。
'Like Professor Zhong Nan Shan, he says, 'it's just as rare.
运动当然非常好，我也爱运动，但是太劳累了，我买过健身卡，基本一年去两三次，还有一次就是健身房关了。
But I'm too tired. I bought a fitness card, went to the gym two or three times a year, and closed the gym once.
运动对我就是周末散步，跑跑，安静休息为主。
Sports for me is the weekend to walk, run, quiet rest-based.
”在极度疲劳的时候，张文宏也爱看比较“无聊”的连续剧，不会太费脑，让自己放松。
"Zhang also likes to watch more" boring "series when he is extremely tired, so he doesn't bother to relax.
“ 我理解什么叫被人欺负张文宏医生平时比较爱阅读，“在焦虑的状态下，看书是非常好的调剂之一。
"I understand what it means to be bullied Dr. Zhang Wenhong, who is usually more likely to read." Reading is one of the great distractions of anxiety.
张文宏还建议，在这个特殊时期，可以读一读科普方面的书。
Zhang also suggested that, at this particular time, you could read books on popular science.
Play“现在社会上有人会觉得自己老是被欺负，其实我一路也是被人欺负过来的，如今年过半百了，现在更理解很多人的这种滋味。
"Now some people in society will feel that they are always bullied, in fact, I have been bullied all the way over, now over 50 years old, now more understand the taste of many people.
书读多了，你能明白欺负人的嘴脸是什么样的，对于欺负你的人你就绕着走，除非你力量强大了。
If you read too much, you can see what a bully's mouth is like, and you can walk around the bully unless you're strong.
被人欺负了，自己更要学会怎么多善待别人，将心比心，换位思考，站在不同的角度看问题。
Be bullied, oneself should learn how to treat others more kindly, empathy, transposition thinking, stand from different point of view.
”自新型冠状病毒疫情发生以来，因坦率有担当的多次发言，张文宏成为备受网友信任的网红“硬核专家”：“把所有人都换下来，共产党员上！”“你在家里不是隔离，也是在战斗！你觉得很闷，闷两个礼拜，病毒也要被你‘闷死’了”“防火防盗防同事”等刷屏级金句火遍网络，也让不少处于紧张慌乱情绪中的民众倍感安心。
Since the outbreak of the new coronavirus, Zhang Wenhong has become a hard core expert trusted by many netizens because of his outspoken statements: "Change everyone off, Communist Party members!" "You feel bored, stuffy for two weeks, the virus will be suffocated by you.
（综合自澎湃新闻见习记者 陈少颖 记者 栾晓娜忻勤 邓朝键、新闻晨报、网友评论等）戳这里进入“全国新型冠状病毒感染病例实时地图”↓↓↓本期编辑 周玉华推荐阅读。
